never large has slipped to about 2000 readers who pay 85 cents 
per copy an issue may carry less than a half page of paid 
advertising 
i am a very bad businessman he admitted 
and he finds himself among a shrinking corps of hungarian 
stalwarts who have resisted the profits of assimilation into 
american culture although he still speaks of returning to hungary 
