members three services credit cards certificates of deposits and 
savings accounts but only the credit card attracted much interest 
overall the credit union had 150 million in assets he said 
under the aarps plan bank one in columbus ohio will issue an 
aarpsponsored visa credit card that will be available to all aarp 
members people who now have credit cards from the credit union 
will automatically become card holders through bank one and be able 
to continue to use their existing cards aarp said 
