drafting the measure had harsh words for andrus 
the organizations president john willke said andrus had bowed 
to the hollow threats and pressure tactics of proabortion 
extremists 
willke called it ridiculous for andrus to continue to claim he 
is prolife when he has vetoed a bill that would have saved 
thousands of lives 
