especially since the frontrunner for the republican gubernatorial 
nomination state sen rachel gilbert of boise voted for the bill 
two of the bills chief architects rep gary montgomery and 
sen roger madsen both republicans said they would refine the 
bill and reintroduce it in the 1991 session 
there are a tremendous amount of people in idaho who are 
prolife madsen said 
