when the bureau as to tell the president how many people live in 
each state and how many members of the house of representatives 
that state is entitled to 
more detailed reports on individual states will be issued 
starting after the first of the year the schedule isnt determined 
yet depending on how well things go in individual states 
those reports will include such information as age sex race 
and household relationships marital status whether people are 
hispanic or not and a variety of housing data 
