sovietrun internment camp he said he believes the camp supplied 
the hundreds of bodies packed together in the nearby forest 
there were youngsters in the camp here not just soldiers i 
was 17 a worker not a soldier he said saturday they gave us 
only bread to eat two hundred and fifty men in one barracks 
