secession 
gorbachev has promised lithuania and other independenceminded 
republics that such a mechanism will be established but the 
measure currently before the soviet legislature gives the kremlin 
final authority on such questions 
on friday nearby estonia pledged to join lithuania in its drive 
to regain independence lost when the soviet union forcibly annexed 
them with latvia the third baltic republic latvia is expected to 
