given to investigating the attempted murder of those on board the 
aircraft any federal violations would be secondary to the state 
police investigation of those charges he said 
fbi agents were at the scene but were not involved in the 
negotiations he said 
the state police will do everything they can to resolve this 
peacefully alford said if it takes a long time to do that 
then well take a long time 
