the hike agreed to by the provincial government would be the 
first in quebec in 20 years quebec university fees are currently 
the lowest in canada 
the demonstration was the latest in a series that has seen 
students occupy the montreal exchange and interrupt a live newscast 
on the french service of the canadian broadcasting corp 
besides the september increase the following year university 
tuition in the province is slated to rise by about the same amount 
making a total increase of about 140 percent 
