only minor injuries 
theres no doubt in my mind the air bags saved them both 
said state police trooper gw dawson who investigated the 
accident the cars were traveling at between 35 and 45 mph 
according to the accident report 
ms van steelant was cited for failure to drive to the right of 
center 
tim hurd a spokesman for the national highway traffic safety 
administration said the crash is believed to be the first accident 
involving two cars equipped with air bags 
beginning with the 1990 model year all cars are required by 
federal law to be equipped with either air bags or automatic seat 
belts 
all chrysler domestic models are equipped with air bags 
